                            <comment id="12929820" author="ryanobjc" created="Mon, 8 Nov 2010 23:42:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;did the rs not recover when the master started?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12929827" author="streamy" created="Mon, 8 Nov 2010 23:49:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think another master became the active one, so they all blocked here indefinitely (he never finished startup).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
